				WeBWorK is the online homework system we will use to practice problem solving. It provides immediate feedback and multiple opportunities to correct mistakes. Assignments reinforce concepts from class and the coursebook. You are encouraged to attempt problems multiple times and to use mistakes as learning opportunities.
			</p>
